				<wikidot:authorName>RockTeethMothEyes</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4022320</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The intention was that there is little known about the guy at this present moment to infer what kind of capture would be best suited since it's still early in the discovery. The fence is meant to keep people away from the primary anomaly while the cameras are meant to observe any additional effects manifested by the secondary.</p> <p>Of course, if this isn't coming across clearly to anyone, I can mess with it.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
