						 <p>A man eats a live rabbit.</p> <p>This is not what I initially intended this to be, but this is what it's become.</p> <p>Valued critters are <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/floppyphoenix" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735419&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1572156747" alt="FloppyPhoenix" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735419)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/floppyphoenix" >FloppyPhoenix</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3487700&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1572156747" alt="Uncle Nicolini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3487700)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" >Uncle Nicolini</a></span>.</p> <p>If you like this, take a trip to my <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/rtme-author">my author page</a>. You might find something else you like there.</p> <p>And of course, thank you for reading.</p> 
